}

Rules:
- Use ONLY relationship types defined in the ontology.
- source must be an entity of an allowed "From" type; target must be an allowed "To" type.
- Include ONLY the attribute keys defined for the specific relationship type plus "evidence". Do NOT add keys not in the ontology.
- "evidence" is REQUIRED and must never be null or empty.
- Do NOT include a "reasoning" field.
